itted with air conditioning so 2,500 temporary cooling units have been fitted in light of concerns about heat in the French capital.\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1623, \"end\": 1629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9629158928688575, \"rank\": 0.023064898137388563, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The village\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"air conditioning\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"2,500 temporary cooling units\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"light\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's superstar swimmerAriarne Titmus believes she has starred in Paris despite the conditionsin the village.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1640, \"end\": 1649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.5739973381344659, \"rank\": 0.7111385587238538, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1712, \"end\": 1717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999998660769, \"rank\": 1.3392160291029619e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the conditionsin\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It probably wasn't the time I thought I was capable of, but living in the Olympic Village makes it hard to perform,' Titmus said recently.\", \"from\": 175