rom\": 2098, \"to\": 2108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is multiple factors that make village life far from ideal,' Magnussen wrote in acolumn for the Australian Daily Telegraph.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2222, \"end\": 2232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.6402268099964847, \"rank\": 0.49109740998508333, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multiple factors\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"village life\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"Magnussen\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"acolumn\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's the cardboard beds, which can not give you optimal sleep.\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cardboard beds\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"optimal sleep\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's the no airconditioning, which is going to play a bigger factor as the week goes.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the no airconditioning\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"a bigger factor\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"the week\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was 20 degrees and raining yesterday.\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"20 degrees\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2419}, {\"ngram\": \"raining\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's going to be mid 30s in the coming days.\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mid 30s\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"the coming days\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'That's going to play a factor